Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton0.Caption: git init
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton0.Hint: This command creates an empty Git repository

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton1.Caption: git status
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton1.Hint: Returns the status of the working directory and the staging environment

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton2.Caption: git add
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton2.Hint: Adds a selected file from your working directory to the Git staging area

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton3.Caption: git add - -all
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton3.Hint: Adds all new or changed files in your working directory to the Git staging area

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton4.Caption: git restore
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton4.Hint: Discard changes that have not yet been committed for a selected file

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton5.Caption: git restore '*'
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton5.Hint: Discard all changes that have not yet been committed

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton6.Caption: git rm - - cached
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton6.Hint: Removes a selected file from the Git staging area.

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton7.Caption: git commit -a -m 'comment'
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton7.Hint: Makes a commit and create a message for the commit in one command

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton8.Caption: git commit
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton8.Hint: Creates a commit with verbose comments, which is like a snapshot of your repository.

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton9.Caption: git commit --amend
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton9.Hint: Change the comment of the last commit

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton10.Caption: git log
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton10.Hint: Lists the commits made in this repository in reverse chronological order.

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton11.Caption: git reset --hard id && git clean -f
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton11.Hint: Jump back to a commit and remove following commits

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton12.Caption: git checkout id
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton12.Hint: Navigate between existing branches using commit-id

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton13.Caption: git checkout branch
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton13.Hint: Switch to the last commit of the specified branch

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton16.Caption: git branch -v
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton16.Hint: Shows the last commit of all branches

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton17.Caption: git merge aBranch
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton17.Hint: Merge a branch with the current branch

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton19.Caption: git diff
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton19.Hint: Show changes since the last commit

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton20.Caption: git diff --name-status
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton20.Hint: Show changed files since the last commit

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton21.Caption: git diff ./aFile
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton21.Hint: Show changes in a specific file since the last commit

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton23.Caption: git diff ID ID --name-status
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton23.Hint: Show changed files between different commits

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton24.Caption: git diff ID ID ./aFile
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton24.Hint: Show changes in a specific file between different commits

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton26.Caption: git diff Branch Branch --name-status
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton26.Hint: Show changed files between different branches

Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton27.Caption: git diff ID ID ./aFile
Tabsheet_0_Commandbutton27.Hint: Show changes in a specific file in different branches
